[0.020, "o", "\u001b[0;1;31m×\u001b[0m hostapd.service - Hostapd IEEE 802.11 AP, IEEE 802.1X/WPA/WPA2/EAP/RADIUS Authenticator\r\n     Loaded: loaded (\u001b]8;;file://archlinux/usr/lib/systemd/system/hostapd.service\u001b\\/usr/lib/systemd/system/hostapd.service\u001b]8;;\u001b\\; \u001b[0;1;32menabled\u001b[0m; preset: \u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mdisabled\u001b[0m)\r\n     Active: \u001b[0;1;31mfailed\u001b[0m (Result: exit-code) since Thu 2026-06-18 21:15:28 WIB; 1min 12s ago\r\n   Duration: 37ms\r\n Invocation: 6d074dcc3df4469382ac94a1a588d4d6\r\n    Process: 840 ExecStart=/usr/bin/hostapd /etc/hostapd/hostapd.conf \u001b[0;1;31m(code=exited, status=1/FAILURE)\u001b[0m\r\n   Main PID: 840 (code=exited, status=1/FAILURE)\r\n   Mem peak: 2M\r\n        CPU: 15ms\r\n\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux systemd[1]: Started Hostapd IEEE 802.11 AP, IEEE 802.1X/WPA/WPA2/EAP/RADIUS Authenticator.\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux hostapd[840]: Line 3390: unknown configuration item 'auth'\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux hostapd[840]: Line 3393: invalid key_mgmt 'WPA_PSK'\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux hostapd[840]: FT (IEEE 802.11r) requires nas_identifier to be configured as a 1..48 octet string\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux hostapd[840]: 3 errors found in configuration file '/etc/hostapd/hostapd.conf'\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux hostapd[840]: Failed to set up interface with /etc/hostapd/hostapd.conf\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux hostapd[840]: Failed to initialize interface\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39mhostapd.service: Main process exited, code=exited, status=1/FAILURE\u001b[0m\r\nJun 18 21:15:28 archlinux systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mhostapd.service: Failed with result 'exit-code'.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
